\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13830909 KR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14232374\charrsid10356450 
Yes, I think so. The - gentry all went to the Church of England. And the - others went to the - well some of them were - went to the - Church of England, but I think the majority that went to the - Congregational were - like the - the - the - carrier an
d the - one part of the - building, there was one family builders, well - some went to church and some went to the Congregational chapel you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid341727 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14232374\charrsid10356450 What about the poorer people, where did they go?
